&lt;p&gt;The School Nursing Special Needs team work with the special schools in Bradford, Keighley and Craven to support and meet the needs of children and young people with additional needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This Staff Nurse role will be based in Skipton and Keighley.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a dynamic, innovative and forward thinking team, always looking to make improvements to ensure children and young people, and their families, are provided with the best care and support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this sounds like a place you would like to work, please apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 8th November&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shortlisting date: 9th November&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview date: 18th November&lt;/p&gt;
